Plain English summary (not legally binding):
- Fantasy Studio is free for personal and non-commercial use forever.
- You can read the source, fork it, modify it, learn from it, and use
  it for personal projects.
- What you cannot do: offer it (or a modified version) as a competing
  commercial product or paid service.
- For commercial licensing, contact FantasyLab AI.
- Four years after the date of first commit, this code automatically
  becomes Apache License, Version 2.0 — fully open source forever.
- Attribution to "Fantasy Studio by FantasyLab AI" is required in any
  derivative work.

